sql_query.sql: SELECT "order_orderdiscount"."offer_id", SUM("order_orderdiscount"."amount") AS "total_discount", (SELECT U0."id" FROM "offer_conditionaloffer" U0 WHERE U0."id" = ("order_orderdiscount"."offer_id") ORDER BY U0."priority" DESC, U0."id" ASC LIMIT 1) AS "offer", COALESCE((SELECT U0."name" FROM "offer_conditionaloffer" U0 WHERE U0."id" = ("order_orderdiscount"."offer_id") ORDER BY U0."priority" DESC, U0."id" ASC LIMIT 1), (SELECT U0."offer_name" FROM "order_orderdiscount" U0 WHERE U0."id" = ("order_orderdiscount"."id") ORDER BY U0."id" ASC LIMIT 1)) AS "display_offer_name" FROM "order_orderdiscount" GROUP BY "order_orderdiscount"."offer_id", 3, 4 ORDER BY 2 DESC
